title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may feel oddly estranged from everything that should be familiar to you today. If so, your experience of alienation is sounding an alarm. Its all too easy to worry about your job, relationships, finances, or even your health. You might struggle to be comfortable, but none of your regular remedies appear to be working now. Instead of adding a new trick or trying a miraculous cure, get out into nature to stir whats truly wild and undomesticated within you. Poet Khalil Gibran wrote, When you reach the end of what you should know, you will be at the beginning of what you should sense. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
